### Cancel Friendship

This endpoint is used to cancel a friendship.

#### Request Body

- `friendship_id`: The ID of the friendship to be removed.


Example:

``` json
{
    "friendship_id": 3
}

 ```

#### Response

The response will be in JSON format with the following schema:

``` json
{
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
        "message": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "success": {
            "type": "boolean"
        }
    }
}

 ```

